<p class="small">The Goodwin University Dental Hygiene program is accredited by the <a href="https://www.ada.org/en/coda/">Commission on Dental Accreditation</a>, a specialized accrediting body recognized by the United States Department of Education.  The Goodwin University Dental Hygiene program has been granted accreditation status as: Approval without reporting requirements.  This accreditation classification is granted to an educational program indicating that the program achieves or exceeds the basic requirements for accreditation.  The Commission on Dental Accreditation can be contacted at (312) 440-4653 or (800) 621-8099 at 211 East Chicago Avenue, Chicago, IL 60611. The Commission's web address is: <a href="https://www.ada.org/en/coda/accreditation">www.ada.org/en/coda/accreditation</a></p>